column5:
#Newline
  • I am here to talk about food calories.
    • #Newline
  • Ask me anything about food calories.
    • #Newline
One serving of whole milk is equal to 1 cup and contains 146 calories.
A plate of Steamed Veg Momos which contains 10 pieces#Comma have 350 calories whereas the fried version contains about 904 calories which is almost triple.
One plate of Steamed Paneer Momos can serve you easily 300 calories. A plate of Fried Paneer Momos has somewhere around 1000-1100 calories.
One plate of Steamed Buff Momos can serve you easily 395 calories.
A plate of steamed Chicken Momos contains 390 calories and a plate of fried Chicken Momos contains 1200 calories. One plate of Fried Chicken Momos covers half of your daily calorie requirement.
A plate of Veg Chowmin contains 273 calories.
A plate of Chicken Chowmin contains 295 calories.
A plate of Chicken Chowmin contains 310 calories.
One bar (162g) of Dark Chocolate contains 884 calories.
A plate of cooked noodles contains 138 calories.
A plate of dry noodles contains 385 calories.
One serving of Thukpa contains 439 calories.
1 bowl of cooked rice has about 136 calories and a plateful of cooked rice has 272 calories which is about 80 grams a plate.
One scoop of regular vanilla ice cream has 137 calories.
One scoop of regular strawberry ice cream has 127 calories.
One scoop of regular chocolate ice cream has 143 calories.
One wedge (approx 1/16 of melon) has 87 calories.
One serving 1 cup (247 g) of Lemonade contains 99 calories.
